Package io.crums.sldg

Class RowIntersection

java.lang.Object
io.crums.sldg.RowIntersection
public class RowIntersection
extends java.lang.Object
A pair of intersecting rows. Since rows in a skip ledger contain hash pointers to previous rows, rows do not necessarily intersect at their own row numbers: they may also intersect at a row referenced by one or both rows' hash pointers.

The relationship, then, between pairs of rows (first(), second()) and instances of this class is one-to-many.

See Also:
type(), PathIntersector
